{"about_the_game":"In this stunning action-platformer, Jordan must traverse an apocalyptic world torn asunder by the great, black rift and its other-worldly monsters to find Ember, the love of his life. Explore a massive, ruined world with imminent threats and an uncertain destiny as you meet interesting NPCs and wield ancient powers to fight foes.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Slay monsters and level up to improve Jordan's stats and create a unique build for your play style.<br></li><li>Collect exotic ingredients and brew them to create custom flask effects to use while exploring and fighting.<br></li><li>Wield powerful weapons of your choice: sword, spear, hammer, and much more.<br></li><li>Channel spells of Crystal, Lucent, Penumbra (and more) from the divine and powerful moon. There are many spells to find and wield.<br></li><li>Collect and equip powerful charms to aid Jordan during combat with unique passive effects.<br></li><li>Explore the randomly generated world as you dive deeper and travel further on this incredible journey under the massive rift to find Ember.<br></li><li>Uncover the secrets of the world as you meet NPCs on their journeys in the apocalyptic world and dive deeper into the extraordinary lore of The Rift Between Us.</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090130/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737573491","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090130/page.bg.jpg?t=1737573491","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090130/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737573491","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090130/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737573491","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_d